        <img src="/ludusmortisgameplay.png" class="centreimage" />
        <figcaption style="text-align:left">A screenshot of the player looking down at their cards. Notice the card up the player's sleeve: this is one of the many ways the player can cheat and gain an advantage.</figcaption>
